The Telegraph - Calcutta
 AIFF asks IFA to show cause
 BY A STAFF REPORTER Calcutta: The All India Football Federation has show-caused the IFA and ordered it to suspend defender Amjad Ali immediately. In a letter received by the IFA on Tuesday, AIFF has asked the state body to explain the unruly behaviour of the Bengal players in the national under-21 football championship final in Jamalpur earlier this month. The AIFF has also slapped a show-cause on Ali for hitting referee M.A. Siddiqui in that game, said IFA secretary Subrata Dutta.  Copyright 
